queryText: select count(*) from "User" u inner join "ListingPreferences" p on p."userId" = u.id

uniqueName: New users by day for last 7 days
queryText: WITH date_series AS (SELECT generate_series(NOW()::date - INTERVAL '6 days', NOW()::date, '1 day')::date AS date) SELECT ds.date, COALESCE(COUNT(u.id), 0) AS signup_count FROM date_series ds LEFT JOIN "User" u ON ds.date = DATE_TRUNC('day', u."createdAt") LEFT JOIN "ListingPreferences" p ON p."userId" = u.id GROUP BY ds.date ORDER BY ds.date ASC;
select count(*) from "Listing" l where l.status = 'BOOKED'
SELECT COUNT(*) FROM "ConversationMessage" cm WHERE cm."createdAt" >= NOW() - INTERVAL '24 HOURS';
